abstract_summ: Coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19), caused by the severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), was first reported in Wuhan, Hubei Province, China in late December 2019 . We re-analysed 640 throat swabs collected from patients with influenza-like-illness from 6 October 2019 to 21 January 2020 .
